OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday sees low cloud and drizzle
OL,7,Finitially, but some brighter spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping later. Sunny spells
OL,9,Fexpected Thursday before evening rain.
OL,10,FRain clears Friday morning, leaving
OL,11,Ffurther sunny spells.
